name: Pawlie n Ester in "Circles"
description:
Part of the Pawlie n Ester artwork series.

This sale is for TWO (2) framed art prints at a special price!

***********************************************************************************************

ABOUT THE PRINTS (each)...
- Paper: 230 gram matte bright white, heavy weight paper.
- Printed using a Canon iX6520 and professional Canon inks, which are perfect for high-quality and long-lasting art prints. 
- Designs are adjusted to allow 1/2" of white space on edges of paper. This allows ease of framing.
- Please be aware that computer monitors are calibrated differently. The color on your screen may differ slightly from the color on the actual print. 
- Each print is made to order. They are individually hand-signed, titled, and dated on the back.
- Copyright 2013 Tonya Newton. Sale of the artwork does not transfer copyright.

ABOUT THE FRAMES (each) ...
- Designed in Sweden. 
- Color: Black. 
- Size: 9 3/4" x 12 1/4".
- Frame: Fiberboard, Foil. 
- Front protection: Polystyrene; makes the frame safer to use, safer to ship, and keeps shipping costs low. 
- Back panel and Photo frame stand (available with the 9 ¾ " x 12 ¼ " frame only): Solid cardboard. 
- Can be used hanging, both horizontally and vertically (depending on the design), to fit in the space available. 
- Flat nail: Steel, Paint. 
- Care instructions: Wipe clean with a dry cloth.

SHIPPING ...
- Shipped together in a cardboard or padded mailer.
- US: USPS Priority Mail shipping. 
- Elsewhere: USPS First-Class Mail.

QUESTIONS ...
- Contact me!
